1
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:36,680
[Eternal Brotherhood 2]

2
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:44,810
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:45,890 --> 00:01:47,990
[Si's Mansion]

4
00:02:04,390 --> 00:02:06,180
Apply the medicine
according to the prescription.

5
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:08,240
Change it twice a day.

6
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,890
When will he wake up?

7
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:16,650
The wound nearly reached
his liver and spleen.

8
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:18,810
He's lucky to be alive.

9
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:22,500
As for when he'll wake up,
it's up to fate.

10
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,680
I see.

11
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,020
When Si Yilin wakes up,

12
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:37,430
let me know immediately.

13
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:38,960
Okay.

14
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:42,470
The assassins have been captured
by the Ministry of War.

15
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:45,329
I'll go back first
to prepare for tomorrow's trial.

16
00:02:54,090 --> 00:02:54,860
I'm sorry.

17
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:10,190
Let me ask you, how is Si Yilin?

18
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,160
He's still unconscious.

19
00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:15,480
Don't worry, My Lord.

20
00:03:15,510 --> 00:03:17,170
He'll live.

21
00:03:23,329 --> 00:03:24,840
Those two people

22
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,890
dared to attack
a Zichuan general in broad daylight.

23
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,910
Such blatant lawlessness

24
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:34,710
must be severely punished without mercy.

25
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,190
Let Di Lin handle the trial.

26
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,920
He'll give a fair judgment.

27
00:03:46,010 --> 00:03:47,100
It's almost time, right?

28
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,829
The water's about to overflow.

29
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,640
When the bubbles are like fish eyes
and faintly audible,

30
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,900
that's the first boil.

31
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:55,680
When they rise
like a string of pearls by the rim,

32
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,829
that's the second.

33
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,960
It's not the time yet.

34
00:04:00,610 --> 00:04:03,090
Only at the third boil will the flavor

35
00:04:03,470 --> 00:04:05,800
truly infuse into the brew.

36
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:08,870
By then, what everyone remembers

37
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:10,710
is the taste of the tea.

38
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:14,120
No one will care about who sold it

39
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,560
or where it came from.

40
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:19,870
Then how do we reach that third boil?

41
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:24,020
As long as we
don't extinguish the fire underneath,

42
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:28,240
we don't need to worry
the tea won't be fully brewed.

43
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:32,240
But Chieftain...

44
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:35,600
I think if Lord Chieftain

45
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:37,230
really wants to take action,

46
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:39,310
after Lord Ge Shan was injured,

47
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,350
those people won't have a chance.

48
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:46,360
Si Yilin has followed
Lord Chieftain for years.

49
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:51,800
They look like father and son,

50
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:56,630
but in fact... they are not that close.

51
00:04:58,990 --> 00:05:00,190
Compared to us,

52
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,310
of course Lord Chieftain

53
00:05:02,450 --> 00:05:04,100
is closer to Si Yilin.

54
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:07,430
But compared to the clan's stability...

55
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:15,560
Gentlemen, the tea is ready.

56
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:54,280
Si Yilin is my subordinate,

57
00:05:57,490 --> 00:05:59,520
but he is also my family.

58
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:03,070
If Si Yilin knows Lord Chieftain

59
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,600
came to see him personally,

60
00:06:04,650 --> 00:06:06,040
he'd be deeply moved.

61
00:06:08,770 --> 00:06:11,170
Thank you
for taking care of him these days.

62
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,650
When he wakes up,

63
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,080
let me know immediately.

64
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,000
Okay.

65
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:34,120
Stop.

66
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,600
I smell some fragrance.

67
00:06:36,750 --> 00:06:37,680
Fragrance?

68
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:53,880
Help!

69
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,480
Stop.

70
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:17,430
You're saying Luo Jie rescued a carriage

71
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,490
of women from Jialai District
from the North Clan?

72
00:07:19,490 --> 00:07:20,290
That's right.

73
00:07:20,990 --> 00:07:23,580
He ran into one of them who had escaped,

74
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,190
and rescued all of them.

75
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:31,990
How do they look?

76
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,040
They are quite attractive.

77
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,270
Are they all married?

78
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:45,510
What does that have to do with you?

79
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:47,240
It has everything to do with me.

80
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,510
Baichuan.

81
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,630
Yes.

82
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:54,310
From now on, those women

83
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:56,480
shall be placed
under top-level protection.

84
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,570
You shall

85
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:00,060
personally oversee everything.

86
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:05,000
Before we arrive in Jialai District,

87
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,720
I want them to be glowing

88
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:07,950
and plump.

89
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:09,800
Send them back to Jialai District?

90
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,870
That's right. We leave tomorrow.

91
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:12,830
Tell everyone:

92
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:13,800
all men

93
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,860
should stay away from that carriage.

94
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,770
Is Lord Xiu
really interested in those women?

95
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,510
They are not just ordinary women.

96
00:08:29,770 --> 00:08:32,900
They're a gift from Heaven—
a key to open Jialai's gates.

97
00:08:34,830 --> 00:08:36,039
It's really Jialai.

98
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,320
We're home.

99
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:38,720
Come. Be careful.

100
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,480
Yeah.

101
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,710
This scene

102
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:42,960
makes me want to recite a poem.

103
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,020
Be careful.

104
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,120
The savior of Jialai.

105
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:51,270
Chief had a point.

106
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:52,960
Control the inner desire,

107
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,760
and you'll control
the hearts of Jialai's people.

108
00:08:57,690 --> 00:08:59,180
I heard

109
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:01,260
Jialai's governor

110
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:03,200
is a young beauty.

111
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,760
Are you sure?

112
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,520
I'm Commander Hu Cheng of Jialai.

113
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:18,450
I express gratitude to you
on behalf of the governor.

114
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:20,160
You're too polite, General.

115
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,550
It's a heroic tale

116
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,680
that we risked our lives

117
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,730
to save those women

118
00:09:23,730 --> 00:09:24,630
from the enemy,

119
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,440
but for the sake of justice,

120
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:29,320
the Yuanzhou Alliance Army
should still be responsible.

121
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,000
Since the governor heard
that you traveled so far

122
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,320
to return the women,

123
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,510
she's been unable to sleep every day.

124
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,990
And she's been thinking
of your kindness every day.

125
00:09:35,990 --> 00:09:38,060
Thanks to King of Light this time,

126
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,600
Jialai...

127
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:43,470
will face a calamity.

128
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:44,280
What?

129
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:47,650
Take them down!

130
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,050
What's going on? What's wrong?

131
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:56,050
We rescued them! How is that wrong?

132
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,090
Rescuing people isn't wrong,

133
00:09:59,090 --> 00:10:00,890
but we rescued the wrong people.

134
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,150
Those women were probably sent

135
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:04,550
as gifts for them.

136
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:09,460
Well, General,

137
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:12,750
I surrender.

138
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,290
You ungrateful bastards!

139
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:31,000
I should have hijacked

140
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,000
all those women!

141
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:33,830
Then you'd have no gifts to give!

142
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,370
I think I can unlock this.

143
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,650
With what? Everything's gone.

144
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,610
Try poking it with this.

145
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,700
That's going to take forever.

146
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:53,000
Chief, what should we do?

147
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:57,320
What else can we do? Sleep.

148
00:11:05,710 --> 00:11:06,830
The governor

149
00:11:06,850 --> 00:11:08,850
wants to interrogate King of Light.

150
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:11,400
-He's here for you.
-He's here for you.

151
00:11:14,570 --> 00:11:15,570
Who's here for me?

152
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:21,680
This is Jialai's specialty,
the ox blood tea.

153
00:11:21,780 --> 00:11:22,040
[Jialai's governor: Pang Xiya]

154
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:24,500
It's specially for honored guests.

155
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:49,160
It indeed tastes good.

156
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,330
It has

157
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,630
a primitive flavor of raw meat and blood.

158
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,000
This is our first meeting,

159
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,390
and you drank the ox blood tea so calmly.

160
00:11:58,030 --> 00:12:01,200
King of Light is indeed
no ordinary person.

161
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,600
I'm flattered.

162
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,580
You invited me to drink tea

163
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:06,790
in your room on our first meeting.

164
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:10,910
Jialai's governor
is no ordinary person as well.

165
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:23,960
My name is Pang Xiya.

166
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,550
My name is King of Light.

167
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:28,980
You can also call me

168
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:31,460
Light, King, or Light King.

169
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,600
King of Light
never reveals his true identity.

170
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:37,890
Always so mysterious.

171
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:41,390
But I respect you.

172
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:48,010
You are the only female governor.

173
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:50,550
And you're imposing. I admire you.

174
00:12:51,310 --> 00:12:55,710
I guess being invited for tea
right after you set foot in Jialai

175
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,830
must make King of Light

176
00:12:58,670 --> 00:13:00,720
a bit nervous.

177
00:13:01,090 --> 00:13:02,020
And I guess

178
00:13:02,230 --> 00:13:04,740
those women were gifts for Lu Di.

179
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:06,810
Unexpectedly, I intercepted them

180
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,630
and returned them openly.

181
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,960
Lu Di must think

182
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:13,270
Jialai has sided

183
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:15,130
with the Yuanzhou Alliance Army.

184
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:16,490
Now you must be

185
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:18,980
more nervous than me.

186
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,070
If I give you to Lu Di,

187
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:24,340
I'll surely be rewarded.
Why should I be nervous?

188
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:27,960
The North Clan

189
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:29,840
has been defeated repeatedly

190
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,570
by the Yuanzhou Alliance Army.

191
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:33,330
You're afraid of offending Lu Di,

192
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,270
and also afraid of taking the wrong side.

193
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:36,330
You invited me to your room

194
00:13:36,330 --> 00:13:38,270
at this hour for tea.

195
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,740
I guess you already have a plan

196
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:42,580
although you're flustered.

197
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:47,820
King of Light, you're indeed
clever and perceptive.

198
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,440
Then I'll be straightforward.

199
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:53,830
Jialai District can be
on friendly terms with the Alliance Army.

200
00:13:53,830 --> 00:13:56,630
We can even pledge allegiance.

201
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,630
I sense a "but" coming.

202
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:07,550
That's right.

203
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:10,970
But you have to marry me.

204
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:17,490
I'm a lazy man.

205
00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:19,480
And I like to bully my subordinates.

206
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:21,150
I often deduct their salaries.

207
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,830
I'll take care of everything at home.

208
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:24,690
And your subordinates' salaries—

209
00:14:24,690 --> 00:14:26,510
Jialai will double them.

210
00:14:26,850 --> 00:14:28,400
I love drinking,

211
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:30,150
especially at pleasure houses.

212
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:32,110
I might not come home for 10 or 15 days.

213
00:14:32,110 --> 00:14:33,370
Jialai has many women,

214
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:34,670
more than anything else.

215
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,600
If you like,

216
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,630
you can have 8 or 10 each night.

217
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:38,550
I promise you won't
see the same face twice in a month.

218
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:39,320
I have two subordinates.

219
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,600
One is knowledgeable,
and the other is skilled in martial arts.

220
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:42,360
The knowledgeable one
knows every military text in history.

221
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:44,440
The other one can take on 10 men at once.

222
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,360
It has to be you.

223
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:49,390
I don't really want to do this either.

224
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:52,050
It's just that every city
that can supply water to Jialai

225
00:14:52,050 --> 00:14:53,790
is under control of the North Clan.

226
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,600
If I can't trust you completely,

227
00:14:55,940 --> 00:14:57,020
I really can't

228
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:59,100
break off with the North Clan.

229
00:15:00,350 --> 00:15:01,830
I can provide water too.

230
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:04,150
Then how are you
any different from the North Clan?

231
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:05,350
If you don't marry me,

232
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:06,860
Jialai can't stand by

233
00:15:06,890 --> 00:15:08,750
the Alliance Army without worry.

234
00:15:09,800 --> 00:15:11,160
Before you arrived,

235
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:13,150
I'd already considered every outcome.

236
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:14,630
The best case:

237
00:15:14,650 --> 00:15:16,510
you fall for me

238
00:15:16,530 --> 00:15:18,330
and propose marriage yourself.

239
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:20,060
The middle ground:

240
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:22,320
we admire each other

241
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:24,750
and have a marriage of convenience.

242
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:29,040
As for the worst case...

243
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,190
Is it to kill me and give me

244
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:33,360
to Lu Di to beg for forgiveness?

245
00:15:33,380 --> 00:15:36,380
I'll give you one day to think it over.

246
00:15:41,050 --> 00:15:42,180
Come on. Bottoms up.

247
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:45,850
Our governor is indeed awesome.

248
00:15:46,010 --> 00:15:48,070
She's made King of Light fall for her.

249
00:15:48,490 --> 00:15:49,330
Of course.

250
00:15:49,810 --> 00:15:50,670
Come on. Drink.

251
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,150
Chief,

252
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:53,750
I think

253
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:55,270
you might as well just marry her.

254
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:56,360
You won't lose out.

255
00:15:56,650 --> 00:15:58,450
If you really can't do it, let me.

256
00:15:59,630 --> 00:16:00,550
Instead of talking nonsense,

257
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:02,150
you should save your energy.

258
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:06,760
My Lord, please come up with a solution.

259
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:09,000
Have you ever heard of a saying—

260
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:13,310
"Fortune favors the virtuous"?

261
00:16:17,580 --> 00:16:19,870
Chief, did you dig that with your eyes?

262
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:22,200
With your head?

263
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:24,890
What Chief meant

264
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,420
is that brain is a handy thing.

265
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:28,020
Remember to use it next time.

266
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:35,000
Come on. Let's go.

267
00:16:35,710 --> 00:16:37,180
Lord Xiu had this all planned
from the start.

268
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,600
You guys escorted the women to Jialai.

269
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,370
I followed you secretly with a team.

270
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:41,830
Even if anything went wrong,

271
00:16:41,830 --> 00:16:43,240
Lord Xiu had the terrain maps ready.

272
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,840
I'd dig a tunnel to save you.

273
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:46,770
Thankfully,
Xiu took precautions in advance.

274
00:16:46,770 --> 00:16:47,520
Otherwise,

275
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:48,960
he would have to marry the governor.

276
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:49,490
Let's go.

277
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,600
The governor is quite good-looking.

278
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:53,720
She's just a bit old.

279
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,080
Good-looking? Her hair's all split ends.

280
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,510
Her skin is dull and not glowing at all.

281
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:57,840
She must have stayed up too late.

282
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,390
You're right.

283
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,960
Who are we?

284
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:09,670
The Xiu... Pretty and attractive.

285
00:17:10,349 --> 00:17:11,470
A perfect match.

286
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:13,619
Brave and resourceful governor,

287
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:16,200
if any of us could marry you,

288
00:17:16,510 --> 00:17:17,109
it would be a blessing

289
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:19,109
for the Yuanzhou Alliance Army.

290
00:17:28,339 --> 00:17:29,740
My dignity has been hurt.

291
00:17:41,710 --> 00:17:42,690
A few days ago,

292
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:47,610
Lord Ge Shan
of the Ministry of Government Supervision

293
00:17:47,650 --> 00:17:50,240
and Lord Si Yilin, the commander
of the Palace Guards,

294
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,570
were both attacked.

295
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:55,370
Lord Ge Shan was slightly injured,

296
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:57,740
while Lord Si Yilin was severely wounded.

297
00:17:57,750 --> 00:18:00,010
The assassins were captured on the spot.

298
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:03,590
They will stand trial today, in public.

299
