-Heroes!

303
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:29,640
Ding Cheng, the evidence against you
for attempted assassination is conclusive.

304
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,440
Do you have anything else to say?

305
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:34,390
During the attack on Ge Shan,

306
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:37,640
we accidentally killed a coachman.

307
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:40,330
