someone you love.

311
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:49,160
So I'm willing to take full responsibility

312
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,150
for his death.

313
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:52,310
As for Lord Si Yilin,

314
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:55,220
he once led us through blood and fire.

315
00:18:55,790 --> 00:18:56,880
I'm very sorry

316
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:59,240
that I had to harm him.

317
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:01,840
But I don't regret it.

318
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:02,720
Very well.

319
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:06,180
Ding Cheng, the culprit,
and Chang Li, an accomplice—

320
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,740
you are guilty of treason and murder.

321
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:12,070
According to Zichuan's law,
I sentence you to death.

322
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:14,890
You'll be executed in three days.

323
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:16,270
I object!

324
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,510
Wayun has stood
as Imperial Capital's shield

325
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:18,920
for centuries.

326
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:21,350
Every son and daughter of Wayun
on the battlefield

327
00:19:21,350 --> 00:19:22,890
disregarded life and death!

328
00:19:22,890 --> 00:19:24,680
But what have we received in return?

329
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:25,440
We've received

330
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,510
weak armies and miserable people!

331
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,480
We lost

332
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:31,160
the 23 districts in Yuanzhou!

333
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:33,790
But Imperial Capital is still crawling

334
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:36,380
with greedy and corrupt officials!

335
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:37,210
That's right!

336
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:40,340
Someone has to shed blood
to wake the world.

337
00:19:41,110 --> 00:19:43,550
Someone has to clear the way
for Zichuan's future.

338
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:45,410
We are willing to be those people.

339
00:19:45,750 --> 00:19:48,750
Even if we die, we die for a worthy cause!

340
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:52,830
-Die without regrets!
-Die without regrets!

341
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:55,600
-Die without regrets!
-Die without regrets!

342
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:57,330
-Die without regrets!
-Die without regrets!

343
00:19:57,330 --> 00:19:58,180
My Lord!

344
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:01,100
This is a petition
signed by 10,000 citizens

345
00:20:01,190 --> 00:20:04,260
from Wayun and Imperial Capital.

346
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,510
They're warriors who have fought bravely

347
00:20:06,510 --> 00:20:08,000
for the clan.

348
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:11,270
They deserve a special pardon!

349
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:22,270
-Pardon!
-Pardon!

350
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:59,160
You're awake. Do you feel any discomfort?

351
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:01,190
What about the two who attacked me?

352
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:05,640
They are still on trial.

353
00:21:11,670 --> 00:21:13,560
Have they been sentenced?

354
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:14,790
Not yet.

355
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:17,240
But just now, Wen He sent a message.

356
00:21:17,310 --> 00:21:18,400
A petition signed

357
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,070
by 10,000 citizens has been delivered,

358
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:21,640
pleading for their pardon.

359
00:21:23,950 --> 00:21:26,440
Given your current condition,
you can't go there.

360
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,590
If there's something you want to say,

361
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:29,540
you can write it down,
and I'll deliver it for you.

362
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:31,230
I have to go myself.

363
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:41,790
My Lord,

364
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:44,120
someone at the trial submitted a petition

365
00:21:44,120 --> 00:21:45,650
signed by 10,000 citizens,

366
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:48,170
requesting clemency for the two assassins.

367
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:03,410
I see.

368
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,700
Looks like you had anticipated this.

369
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:11,810
How dare you!

370
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:13,540
You two

371
00:22:13,940 --> 00:22:15,550
are guilty of treason and murder!

372
00:22:15,550 --> 00:22:17,200
And you've incited the public!

373
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,350
Your crimes are even more heinous!

374
00:22:18,350 --> 00:22:21,480
According to Zichuan's law,
you shall hang yourselves!

375
00:22:21,730 --> 00:22:22,920
Execute immediately!

376
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:24,480
You're all in this together!

377
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:26,750
If you won't release them,
we'll save them ourselves!

378
00:22:26,750 --> 00:22:27,900
-Save them!
-Save them!

379
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:29,340
-Save them!
-Save them!

380
00:22:29,370 --> 00:22:30,970
Anyone who obstructs the law

381
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,470
will be punished as an accomplice!

382
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:35,960
-Release them!
-Release them!

383
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:36,720
Let me go!

384
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:37,830
Let me go!

385
00:22:37,830 --> 00:22:38,590
I'm not guilty!

386
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:40,110
-Release them!
-Release them!

387
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,830
Let go! Let go of me!

388
00:22:42,110 --> 00:22:43,160
Wait!

389
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,890
-Release them!
-Release them!

390
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:49,790
Di Lin.

391
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:51,590
What are you doing here?

392
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:52,920
I have something to say.

393
00:22:52,930 --> 00:22:54,260
Please give me a moment.

394
00:22:59,120 --> 00:23:01,120
As the plaintiff in this case,

395
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:04,430
I want to withdraw the charges

396
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:08,480
and request leniency.

397
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:14,960
I am the commander of the Palace Guards.

398
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:20,310
My soldiers love and trust me,

399
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:23,000
but I failed to lead them

400
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:26,000
to bring victory back to Zichuan.

401
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:28,990
That is my dereliction of duty.

402
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:39,040
I bear the responsibility.

403
00:23:39,270 --> 00:23:42,270
I failed to maintain order in Zichuan,

404
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:45,510
causing Lord Ge's injuries.

405
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:48,590
And I made the people want to rebel!

406
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:51,220
That is my negligence!

407
00:24:23,310 --> 00:24:24,350
Therefore,

408
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:29,740
I'll take responsibility for their crimes.

409
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:35,450
I deserved that stab.

410
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,750
But it doesn't mean I forgive you.

411
00:24:56,130 --> 00:24:58,480
Nor does it mean you're not at fault.

412
00:25:09,590 --> 00:25:11,880
I just want you to understand

413
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:17,900
you can't escape
the consequences of defeat.

414
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:24,350
I know you're disappointed in Zichuan.

415
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:26,310
You want Zichuan

416
00:25:26,310 --> 00:25:29,680
to be a fair and strong clan.

417
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:32,330
But with the North Clan still a threat,

418
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:35,170
you can't turn your blades

419
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:38,700
against your own people.

420
00:25:45,740 --> 00:25:47,070
If you really think

421
00:25:47,090 --> 00:25:48,970
that my death

422
00:25:50,810 --> 00:25:53,810
can solve this problem,

423
00:25:58,310 --> 00:26:00,560
I'm willing to sacrifice myself.

424
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:15,860
Warriors.

425
00:26:18,730 --> 00:26:20,080
Brothers!

426
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:25,920
You all have shed blood for this clan.

427
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,070
So what is this clan?

428
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:35,790
It's your home!

429
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:38,800
A home

430
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:42,510
will never abandon its people.

431
00:26:42,580 --> 00:26:46,960
Nor will it ever abandon its lands!

432
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:52,020
Eventually,

433
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:57,460
you will have

434
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:59,600
the respect and dignity

435
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:04,000
you deserve.

436
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:06,360
-Well said!
-Well said!

437
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,600
That's right!

438
00:27:07,630 --> 00:27:08,390
Well said!

439
00:27:08,600 --> 00:27:09,270
That's right!

440
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:10,420
Well said!

441
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,350
Well said!

442
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:15,340
Di Lin.

443
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:25,730
The law is the law.
Crimes must be punished.

444
00:27:26,370 --> 00:27:27,330
But Di Lin,

445
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,990
this is our own problem.

446
00:27:30,510 --> 00:27:32,710
But justice can be tempered with mercy!

447
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,330
-My Lord.
-My Lord.

448
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,200
Release them!

449
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,400
Release them now!

450
00:27:38,590 --> 00:27:39,550
Release them!

451
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:40,830
Release them now!

452
00:27:49,050 --> 00:27:50,650
Justice tempered with mercy

453
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:53,880
is the very spirit of law.

454
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:58,440
They did something wrong,

455
00:27:58,810 --> 00:28:00,550
but they did it for a reason.

456
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:04,440
And Si Yilin has withdrawn the charges,

457
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:06,550
requesting clemency.

458
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:10,960
As for the compensation
and the restoration of Wayun,

459
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:15,300
the clan will give you an explanation.

460
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:21,930
-Long live the chieftain!
-Long live the chieftain!

461
00:28:26,850 --> 00:28:27,530
Lord Ge.

462
00:28:34,370 --> 00:28:35,440
Lord Si Yilin,

463
00:28:35,860 --> 00:28:38,120
there's something I'd like to say to you.

464
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:42,630
A kind heart can't tame wolves.

465
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:46,450
I had no choice. I'm a soldier.

466
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:49,310
Foolish one.

467
00:28:59,730 --> 00:29:02,690
My Lord, you were put
in a difficult position today.

468
00:29:03,830 --> 00:29:05,830
Lord Chieftain's presence made you

469
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:08,040
a villain who punished the heroes.

470
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,550
Our chieftain, Lord Canxing,

471
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:16,790
sees clearer than anyone.

472
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:19,350
He's the one
who asked me to handle the case.

473
00:29:19,350 --> 00:29:21,130
He's also the one
who asked me to release them.

474
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:22,400
Thus,

475
00:29:22,430 --> 00:29:25,630
the Three Central Offices
will no longer act recklessly.

476
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:29,750
I've become the heartless one
in the people's eyes,

477
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:31,210
while he has won the people's hearts

478
00:29:31,210 --> 00:29:32,490
and saved his dignity.

479
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,680
The law can be bent

480
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:36,330
due to his words.

481
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:37,640
Fairness and justice

482
00:29:39,890 --> 00:29:42,290
are not as important as political balance.

483
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:44,110
Our Lord Chieftain

484
00:29:44,330 --> 00:29:46,260
has placed everyone over the fire,

485
00:29:47,230 --> 00:29:48,990
while he stays untouched.

486
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,570
Lord Chieftain,

487
00:29:53,070 --> 00:29:55,530
the refugee crisis
spiraled out of control.

488
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:57,350
Everyone has been punished.

489
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,010
As their commander,

490
00:29:59,010 --> 00:30:00,790
I should accept severer punishment.

491
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:02,590
Indeed, you should be punished.

492
00:30:07,450 --> 00:30:09,140
I accept the punishment.

493
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:11,570
Do you know why you should be punished?

494
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:14,170
Not because you did something wrong,

495
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:18,090
but because we need to give
an explanation to the people.

496
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:22,400
You'll be suspended.

497
00:30:23,070 --> 00:30:24,640
Someone else will handle the affairs

498
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:27,100
at the Ministry of Government Supervision.

499
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:30,550
We can't attack the Liufeng family now.

500
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:34,290
When there are too many refugees,
they'll become vagrants.

501
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:36,470
Once vagrants become bandits,

502
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:40,310
the world will fall into chaos.

503
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:43,690
Everything you said before was correct.

504
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,840
Thank you, Lord Chieftain.

505
00:30:51,060 --> 00:30:52,060
Our priority now

506
00:30:52,450 --> 00:30:54,740
is to comfort the refugees.

507
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:56,240
I understand.

508
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,200
Then I'll take my leave.

509
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:06,720
Okay.

510
00:31:16,470 --> 00:31:17,400
Lord Chieftain,

511
00:31:17,970 --> 00:31:19,950
I thank you on behalf of the people.

512
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:21,810
Safe journey.

513
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,920
Doctor, how is my father?

514
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,560
This is a case of atrophy.

515
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,790
His limbs are weak and feeble,

516
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:36,440
unable to be used for now.

517
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,960
My prescription

518
00:31:37,990 --> 00:31:40,680
can only delay the decline.

519
00:31:41,060 --> 00:31:43,380
If it worsens to the point
where he can't speak,

520
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:46,290
there'll be nothing we can do.

521
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:47,580
Is there really...

522
00:31:49,550 --> 00:31:51,150
Is there really no other way?

523
00:31:51,390 --> 00:31:53,190
As long as you can cure my father,

524
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:55,110
the Liufeng family
will reward you handsomely.

525
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:57,240
Doctor, please figure something out.

526
00:31:57,400 --> 00:31:58,400
Help her.

527
00:31:59,510 --> 00:32:01,590
I do have an ancient prescription.

528
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:04,440
But it's said
it's hard to find the medicine.

529
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,680
Even if you find it,

530
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:08,110
I'm not sure if I can cure him or not.

531
00:32:08,130 --> 00:32:09,130
No matter what,

532
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,690
I'm willing to give it a try.

533
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:24,260
The peak of the mountain,
the horn of the dragon.

534
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:29,200
Where heaven and earth bleed,
swallows return home.

535
00:32:31,270 --> 00:32:32,400
What does that mean?

536
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,780
Doctor, thank you for your guidance.

537
00:32:47,790 --> 00:32:49,270
What did he mean?

538
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:50,790
What he meant is

539
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,750
the medicine is in the far east.

540
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:55,450
The prescription is written on the paper.

541
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:58,550
It depends on you whether you can get it.

542
00:33:03,270 --> 00:33:05,310
Now that I know the general direction,

543
00:33:05,310 --> 00:33:06,550
I'll go find it myself.

544
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:07,550
I'll go with you.

545
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:10,000
You're an elder of the Lin family.

546
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,930
I can't waste any more of your time.

547
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:13,890
When I come back with the medicine,

548
00:33:13,890 --> 00:33:15,290
I'll thank you properly.

549
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:16,680
It's a promise then.

550
00:33:16,790 --> 00:33:17,510
A promise.

551
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:28,660
They say a wise man
submits to circumstances.

552
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:30,350
In my opinion,

553
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:34,200
King of Light, you're the wisest of all.

554
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:38,770
They also say the prettier a woman is,

555
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:40,300
the sharper her mind is.

556
00:33:40,550 --> 00:33:43,120
Governor, you are also impressive.

557
00:33:43,140 --> 00:33:45,410
Aren't we a perfect match then?

558
00:33:45,510 --> 00:33:46,050
No.

559
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:48,060
The more alike two people are,

560
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:49,920
the more likely they are

561
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,440
to clash.

562
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,440
So,

563
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:56,480
you don't like any of these robes?

564
00:33:56,820 --> 00:33:58,690
They're too flashy.

565
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,460
They don't match my style.

566
00:34:00,590 --> 00:34:01,460
I'm

567
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:03,830
a low-profile and extravagant person.

568
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,310
Why don't we hear

569
00:34:06,310 --> 00:34:08,070
what your subordinates think?

570
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:10,150
They've followed you for so long.

571
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:12,719
They must know your preferences well.

572
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:17,040
I think the first one is good—

573
00:34:17,510 --> 00:34:18,570
noble and elegant.

574
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,460
This is not about which one is good.

575
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:26,320
In my opinion, they're all great.

576
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,920
It's like they're tailored for him.

577
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:33,310
My Lord, choose whatever you like.

578
00:34:33,310 --> 00:34:34,639
I'm not afraid of death!

579
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:38,469
But I know you definitely won't do that.

580
00:34:38,469 --> 00:34:39,239
Shut up.

581
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:40,850
One more word

582
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:42,210
and I'll walk out naked!

583
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,340
That sounds good too. I like that.

584
00:34:44,969 --> 00:34:48,270
No. I think the first one is good.

585
00:34:49,190 --> 00:34:50,670
My Lord!

586
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:54,690
Water's seeping into the dungeon!

587
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:13,540
My Lord, after so many years with you,

588
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:16,630
I'm truly reluctant to part from you.

589
00:35:16,630 --> 00:35:17,660
But at the thought

590
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:21,550
that you're finally going
to be someone else's trouble,

591
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:23,320
I'm somewhat relieved.

592
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,480
I bade you farewell by the river.

593
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:28,630
You're already married when you return.

594
00:35:28,630 --> 00:35:29,960
I never expected

595
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:31,910
that Lord Xiu is getting married.

596
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,860
I didn't expect it either.

597
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,840
All these years,

598
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:39,960
I always thought

599
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:42,290
you were too heartless for love to matter.

600
00:35:43,630 --> 00:35:46,360
I never expected you
to have such a relationship.

601
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:49,620
I'm so frustrated.

602
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,110
How did I suddenly

603
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:52,440
become such a crybaby?

604
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,050
Chief.

605
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:02,580
I hope in the future, when you get drunk,

606
00:36:02,610 --> 00:36:04,140
someone will take you home.

607
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:05,230
When you earn money,

608
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:06,360
don't hand it all over.

609
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:08,110
Keep some for yourself.

610
00:36:11,730 --> 00:36:13,330
I can't bear to part from you.

611
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:16,400
I can't go on.

612
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:38,530
Well, why are you crying?

613
00:36:40,430 --> 00:36:41,200
Stop crying.

614
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:43,090
Chief!

615
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,440
Is the Xiu Battalion

616
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:48,730
going to break up just like this?

617
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:51,920
I'm so sad.

618
00:36:54,730 --> 00:36:55,720
Don't be sad.

619
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,710
I'm sad too. I'm heartbroken.

620
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:00,890
I never thought I, the Flower of Yuanzhou,

621
00:37:00,890 --> 00:37:01,890
would now...

622
00:37:01,910 --> 00:37:02,770
King of Light!

623
00:37:20,710 --> 00:37:21,970
Did you dig the tunnel?

624
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:23,970
Why did you choose that location?

625
00:37:24,030 --> 00:37:26,030
I did it to save Chief.

626
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:30,360
The earth near the underground river
is soft. It's easy to dig.

627
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:32,700
There really is
an underground river beneath Jialai?

628
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:34,960
You've solved the water source problem?

629
00:37:35,130 --> 00:37:36,310
We've been under the control
of the North Clan

630
00:37:36,310 --> 00:37:37,500
because of the water shortage.

631
00:37:37,500 --> 00:37:39,710
Can you find another location
to drill for water?

632
00:37:39,710 --> 00:37:40,480
He's my subordinate.

633
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,920
I'll answer your question.

634
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,630
Xiya, I...

635
00:37:42,630 --> 00:37:43,440
Call me Governor.

636
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:44,920
We're not that close.

637
00:37:47,670 --> 00:37:49,510
It shouldn't be a problem.

638
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:50,850
That's great.

639
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:52,460
If we can break free from their control

640
00:37:52,460 --> 00:37:53,930
over the water source,

641
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:55,280
my people

642
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:57,340
will no longer be at the mercy of them.

643
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:59,870
Jialai's independence
will be within reach.

644
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:04,160
Come on, get up.

645
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,800
Stop crying. Sit.

646
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:11,000
If Li Nong solves

647
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,590
the water source issue,

648
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:16,200
does that mean
we don't have to get married?

649
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:18,120
With water, who'd still want you?

650
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:19,480
Wake up.

651
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:30,210
I suddenly feel a bit upset.

652
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:32,550
It's like I bought a rope to hang myself,

653
00:38:32,550 --> 00:38:33,350
but suddenly,

654
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:35,460
the rope broke.

655
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,960
Still, you helped Jialai find the key

656
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:41,520
to breaking free from their control.

657
00:38:41,700 --> 00:38:43,270
It's credited to you.

658
00:38:45,730 --> 00:38:48,200
So, if Li Nong stays

659
00:38:48,230 --> 00:38:50,490
to help you solve the water source issue,

660
00:38:51,720 --> 00:38:54,650
does that mean
the Yuanzhou Alliance Army and Jialai

661
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:57,350
have reached an agreement?

662
00:38:58,110 --> 00:38:58,850
Of course.

663
00:38:58,950 --> 00:39:01,190
Good. It's a pleasure working with you.

664
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:13,460
Come on.

665
00:39:23,030 --> 00:39:26,360
Hello. Don't be afraid.

666
00:39:26,630 --> 00:39:27,990
I just want to ask

667
00:39:28,870 --> 00:39:30,710
if you know what this note

668
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:31,840
means.

669
00:39:37,470 --> 00:39:38,390
I don't know.

670
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:42,030
Are you from the North Clan
or the Alliance Army?

671
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:44,130
Don't talk to the people riding horses.

672
00:39:44,130 --> 00:39:45,120
If we run into the North Clan's men,

673
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:46,180
we'll be arrested.

674
00:39:48,030 --> 00:39:48,750
Sister,

675
00:39:48,850 --> 00:39:51,010
go ask Elder Budan at the sacred temple.

676
00:39:51,010 --> 00:39:52,210
He knows everything.

677
00:39:52,390 --> 00:39:53,320
Hurry, let's go.

678
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,640
Okay, thank you.

679
00:40:26,190 --> 00:40:28,930
I, Lin Yu, request an audience
with Elder Budan.

680
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:30,620
Are you from the west?

681
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:32,510
Yes.

682
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,300
He's been waiting for you.

683
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:43,810
The peak of the mountain,
the horn of the dragon.

684
00:40:45,130 --> 00:40:48,060
Where heaven and earth bleed,
swallows return home.

685
00:40:57,220 --> 00:40:58,620
Let me ask you a question.

686
00:40:59,070 --> 00:41:00,070
Go ahead.

687
00:41:01,090 --> 00:41:02,700
To cure your father,

688
00:41:03,740 --> 00:41:05,540
would you harm innocent people?

689
00:41:06,330 --> 00:41:07,210
Of course not.

690
00:41:07,850 --> 00:41:09,650
My father has taught me since childhood

691
00:41:09,650 --> 00:41:11,900
that villains must be punished,

692
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:14,540
but the innocent must never be harmed.

693
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:17,000
Now I can answer your question.

694
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:21,800
Many people know the meaning

695
00:41:22,230 --> 00:41:23,760
of this note,

696
00:41:24,360 --> 00:41:25,510
including me.

697
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:27,690
But those who can decipher

698
00:41:27,690 --> 00:41:29,550
the positive meaning of this note

699
00:41:30,720 --> 00:41:33,400
might only mislead you.

700
00:41:34,190 --> 00:41:34,880
Mislead?

701
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:37,480
You are a kind person.

702
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,610
Among Ke City, Jialai,

703
00:41:40,630 --> 00:41:42,030
and Pingyang District,

704
00:41:42,220 --> 00:41:43,630
there are a few mountain passes

705
00:41:43,630 --> 00:41:44,760
with lax management.

706
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:47,290
Smuggling of forbidden items
happens there.

707
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,580
There,

708
00:41:49,570 --> 00:41:51,500
you may find clues to what you seek.

709
00:42:04,330 --> 00:42:06,810
Thank you. I'll set out immediately.

710
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:21,550
Elder,

711
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:23,790
this could harm the Dragon Race.

712
00:42:24,210 --> 00:42:25,920
Why did you still guide her?

713
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:28,340
This is fate.

714
00:42:30,710 --> 00:42:32,960
She will walk towards the light.

715
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:35,670
I've compiled

716
00:42:35,670 --> 00:42:38,030
the water distribution
and redirection methods near Jialai.

717
00:42:38,030 --> 00:42:40,070
I put them into a booklet
with illustrations.

718
00:42:40,070 --> 00:42:41,730
Please take a look, Governor.

719
00:42:45,350 --> 00:42:46,010
Have a seat.

720
00:42:53,380 --> 00:42:53,980
Sit!

721
00:42:56,880 --> 00:42:59,590
It's clear, detailed,
and easy to understand.

722
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:02,930
Let's get to the main point.

723
00:43:03,510 --> 00:43:05,230
Most of the districts in Yuanzhou

724
00:43:05,230 --> 00:43:06,760
are under the control of the North Clan.

725
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:09,400
It's not just a matter
of weak military strength.

726
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,550
The main reason is

727
00:43:10,790 --> 00:43:13,170
they don't have sufficient resources.

728
00:43:13,810 --> 00:43:16,100
If we could share the technology
of water sourcing and irrigation

729
00:43:16,100 --> 00:43:17,300
across Yuanzhou,

730
00:43:18,060 --> 00:43:20,490
maybe we could
help them change their fate.

731
00:43:21,100 --> 00:43:23,700
But promoting it
to so many districts one by one

732
00:43:23,950 --> 00:43:25,510
would take too much time.

733
00:43:26,060 --> 00:43:28,710
So, I want to host a banquet

734
00:43:28,710 --> 00:43:30,070
in Jialai.

735
00:43:30,590 --> 00:43:31,590
We'll invite the envoys

736
00:43:31,590 --> 00:43:33,990
not under the control of the North Clan

737
00:43:34,020 --> 00:43:35,680
to learn the technology here.

738
00:43:35,720 --> 00:43:37,220
We can also take this opportunity

739
00:43:37,220 --> 00:43:39,970
to unite all of Yuanzhou.

740
00:43:46,060 --> 00:43:47,790
It's an excellent idea.

741
00:43:48,510 --> 00:43:50,300
Water is essential.

742
00:43:50,370 --> 00:43:52,350
Now that the water source issue
can be solved,

743
00:43:52,350 --> 00:43:53,950
I believe no one would say no.

744
00:43:53,950 --> 00:43:54,720
Yeah.

745
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:59,460
But...
since you'll host a banquet in Jialai,

746
00:43:59,480 --> 00:44:02,000
it wouldn't be too much if I charge you

747
00:44:02,030 --> 00:44:03,360
some venue fees, right?

748
00:44:07,100 --> 00:44:09,750
You really don't make any deal at a loss.

749
00:44:10,330 --> 00:44:11,520
But I like that.

750
00:44:12,190 --> 00:44:13,000
In that case,

751
00:44:13,930 --> 00:44:16,060
I'll charge you some tuition fees too.

752
00:44:18,060 --> 00:44:19,370
In my name,

753
00:44:19,610 --> 00:44:21,610
send invitations to the districts.

754
00:44:22,020 --> 00:44:23,550
Jialai will host a banquet.

755
00:44:34,070 --> 00:44:34,640
Good.

756
00:44:49,080 --> 00:44:49,760
Good.
